channel.title: Help, Urgently
channel.description:
Ok, I'm stuck. im trying to make my server online
I have uTorrent. when I run uTorrent first I get this error when I run my server [code]Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use?[/code]
and when I run my server first I get this error [code][2008-11-07 15:09:46] TCP port bind failed 0.0.0.0:43594: (10048) Only one usage of each socket address (protocol/network address/port) is normally permitted.[/code]
This is the only way to run my server because I cant portforward because I have no router. I have modem :( HELP PLEASE
